ow to Get Started</h2>\nIn order to build a custom audience from people who have purchased from you or<strong>visited your website</strong>(which are some of the best kind of people by the way  it makes sense, theyve raised their hand and shown an interest in what you have to offer as a business), you need install a<strong>Facebook Pixel</strong>.\n\n<i>*This part you might need to be a little technically inclined for or send this guide to someone who is.</i>\n\n</div>\n<blockquote>How to Install your Facebook Pixel (Free Guide)\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/business/help/952192354843755\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.facebook.com/business/help/952192354843755</a></blockquote>\n<i>The page will look something like this:</i>\n\n</div>\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-5042 size-full\" src=\"http://codelabstudios.com/app/uploads/2018/02/Facebook-Pixel-Guide-min.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"728\" height=\"447\" />\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n&nbsp;\n<h5 id=\"Audience\">How to Create the Audience</h5>\n<blockquote><span class=\"popout\">Visit your Facebook Ads Manager\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ads/manager/\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.facebook.com/business/help/952192354843755</a></span></blockquote>\nOnce youre in your<strong>Facebook Ads Manager</strong>, go ahead and click on the<img src=\"https://codelabstudios.dev/app/uploads/2017/08/Hamburger.jpg\" />and follow the instructions in the images below.\n\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-5041\" src=\"http://codelabstudios.com/app/uploads/2018/02/Steps-1-and-2-min.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"734\" height=\"268\" />\n\nAnd thats basically it for the basics on setting up a custom audience for remarketing.\n\n<hr />\n\n<h6 id=\"Conclusion\">Conclusion</h6>\nThis is just the beginners guide on<strong>what is Facebook Remarketing &amp; How to get Started</strong>. It gets complicated from here when it comes down to targeting the audience, creating ads, A/B testing campaigns, optimizing for conversions, getting people to actually buy from you, and scaling up. If youre not careful, you can waste money.\n<blockquote><span class=\"popout\">If Facebook Advertising sounds like something youd want to look into, give us a call and get some free advice.</span></blockquote>\n&nbsp;','What is Facebook Remarketing and is it Important?','','inherit','closed','closed','','4191-autosave-v1','','','2018-02-14 05:20:54','2018-02-14 10:20:54','',4191,'http://codelabstudios.com/4191-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(5040,1,'2018-02-14 05:12:55','2018-02-14 10:12:55','','Facebook-Remarketing-for-Local-Businesses-min-1','','inherit','open','closed','','facebook-remarketing-for-local-businesses-min-1','','','2018-02-14 05:14:31','2018-02-14 10:14:31','',4191,'http://codelabstudios.com/app/uploads/2018/02/Facebook-Remarketing-for-Local-Businesses-min-1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(5041,1,'2018-02-14 05:13:34','2018-02-14 10:13:34','','Steps-1-and-2-min','','inherit','open','closed','','steps-1-and-2-min','','','2018-02-14 05:18:11','2018-02-14 10:18:11','',4191,'http://codelabstudios.com/app/uploads/2018/02/Steps-1-and-2-min.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(5042,1,'2018-02-14 05:13:34','2018-02-14 10:13:34','','Facebook-Pixel-Guide-min','','inherit','open','closed','','facebook-pixel-guide-min','','','2018-02-14 05:17:12','2018-02-14 10:17:12','',4191,'http://codelabstudios.com/app/uploads/2018/02/Facebook-Pixel-Guide-min.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(5043,1,'2018-02-14 05:15:56','2018-02-14 10:15:56','<header class=\"entry-header\">\r\n<h1 class=\"entry-title\">What is Facebook Remarketing and is it Important?</h1>\r\n</header>\r\n<div class=\"entry-content content\">\r\n<div id=\"cs-content\" class=\"cs-content\">\r\n<div id=\"x-section-1\" class=\"x-section\">\r\n<div class=\"x-container max width\">\r\n<div class=\"x-column x-sm x-1-1\">\r\n<div class=\"x-text\">\r\n\r\nSo if youre interested in advertising on Facebook in 2017, you<strong>should first know</strong>about Facebook Remarketing, Why its amazing, and how to utilize it. Ill explain all of this for you below.\r\n\r\n<strong><u>The quickest way to explain it is with this example;</u></strong>\r\n\r\nImagine you walked into your local coffee shop today.\r\n\r\nFor some reason you didnt buy anything, maybe you had to take a call, your house was on fire, it can be anything. You left the shop.\r\n\r\nThat coffee shop lost a potential customer.<strong>Until now.</strong>\r\n\r\nAs youre on your way home, all the billboards you pass by, actually have your local coffee shop advertising on them.\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-5040\" src=\"http://codelabstudios.com/app/uploads/2018/02/Facebook-Remarketing-for-Local-Businesses-min-1-300x187.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"187\" />\r\n\r\nNot only are you seeing their ads but youre seeing offers that are<strong>relevant and enticing to you</strong> the potential customer.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<blockquote>Now that business has more plenty of opportunities to bring you back in as a customer. Its a game-changer.</blockquote>\r\n<div id=\"x-section-1\" class=\"x-section\">\r\n<div class=\"x-container max width\">\r\n<div class=\"x-column x-sm x-1-1\">\r\n<div class=\"x-text\">\r\n\r\nBasically, Facebook can do just this, except for online advertising (and even offline to some degree).\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"x-section-2\" class=\"x-section\">\r\n<div class=\"x-container max width\">\r\n<div class=\"x-column x-sm x-1-1\">\r\n<div class=\"x-text\"></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2 id=\"Remarketing\">What is Facebook Remarketing?</h2>\r\n<strong>Facebook Remarketing refers to the strategy of displaying ads, offers, and discounts, to people that have visited your website</strong>(making them potential customers),<strong>while theyre browsing Facebook</strong>.\r\n\r\nYou can even display ads to people who have purchased from you in the past. Display up-sells, cross-sells, etc and bring them back to your site every time.\r\n\r\nAnyone that visits your website can automatically be put into whats called a<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/business/help/341425252616329\"><strong>Facebook Custom Audience</strong></a>(and then into a Remarketing List).\r\n<blockquote><span class=\"box\"><span id=\"item\"><a href=\"https://emailoctopus.com/\">What is a Facebook Custom Audience?</a></span>\r\nA Custom Audience from a customer list is a type of audience you can create made up of your existing customers. You can target ads to the audience youve created on Facebook, Instagram, and Audience Network.</span>\r\n\r\n<i>Source: Facebook Help Center</i></blockquote>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','What is Facebook Remarketing and is it Important?','','inherit','closed','closed','','4191-revision-v1','','','2018-02-14 05:15:56','2018-02-14 10:15:56','',4191,'http://codelabstudios.com/4191-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(5044,1,'2018-02-14 05:18:47','2018-02-14 10:18:47','<header class=\"entry-header\">\r\n<h1 class=\"entry-title\">What is Facebook Remarketing and is it Important?</h1>\r\n</header>\r\n<div class=\"entry-content content\">\r\n<div id=\"cs-content\" class=\"cs-content\">\r\n<div id=\"x-section-1\" class=\"x-section\">\r\n<div class=\"x-container max width\">\r\n<div class=\"x-column x-sm x-1-1\">\r\n<div class=\"x-text\">\r\n\r\nSo if youre interested in advertising on Facebook in 2017, you<strong>should first know</strong>about Facebook Remarketing, Why its amazing, and how to utilize it. Ill explain all of this for you below.\r\n\r\n<strong><u>The quickest way to explain it is with this example;</u></strong>\r\n\r\nImagine you walked into your local coffee shop today.\r\n\r\nFor some reason you didnt buy anything, maybe you had to take a call, your house was on fire, it can be anything. You left the shop.\r\n\r\nThat coffee shop lost a potential customer.<strong>Until now.</strong>\r\n\r\nAs youre on your way home, all the billboards you pass by, actually have your local coffee shop advertising on them.\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-5040 size-full\" src=\"http://codelabstudios.com/app/uploads/2018/02/Facebook-Remarketing-for-Local-Businesses-min-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"724\" height=\"451\" />\r\n\r\nNot only are you seeing their ads but youre seeing offers that are<strong>relevant and enticing to you</strong> the potential customer.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<blockquote>Now that business has more plenty of opportunities to bring you back in as a customer. Its a game-changer.</blockquote>\r\n<div id=\"x-section-1\" class=\"x-section\">\r\n<div class=\"x-container max width\">\r\n<div class=\"x-column x-sm x-1-1\">\r\n<div class=\"x-text\">\r\n\r\nBasically, Facebook can do just this, except for online advertising (and even offline to some degree).\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"x-section-2\" class=\"x-section\">\r\n<div class=\"x-container max width\">\r\n<div class=\"x-column x-sm x-1-1\">\r\n<div class=\"x-text\"></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2 id=\"Remarketing\">What is Facebook Remarketing?</h2>\r\n<strong>Facebook Remarketing refers to the strategy of displaying ads, offers, and discounts, to people that have visited your website</strong>(making them potential customers),<strong>while theyre browsing Facebook</strong>.\r\n\r\nYou can even display ads to people who have purchased from you in the past. Display up-sells, cross-sells, etc and bring them back to your site every time.\r\n\r\nAnyone that visits your website can automatically be put into whats called a<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/business/help/341425252616329\"><strong>Facebook Custom Audience</strong></a>(and then into a Remarketing List).\r\n<blockquote><span class=\"box\"><span id=\"item\"><a href=\"https://emailoctopus.com/\">What is a Facebook Custom Audience?</a></span>\r\nA Custom Audience from a customer list is a type of audience you can create made up of your existing customers. You can target ads to the audience youve created on Facebook, Instagram, and Audience Network.</span>\r\n\r\n<i>Source: Facebook Help Center</i></blockquote>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"Importance\">Why is this so important?</h3>\r\nNow heres the fun part.\r\n\r\n<strong>Anytime someone visits your website, they are anonymously saved to your custom audience.</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Then, the next time they are on Facebook, they are going to see YOUR ADS in their news feed or side bar.</strong>\r\n\r\nMost people are on Facebook at some point these days, including your target customer, roughly<strong>2 billion people/month</strong>log on.\r\n\r\nSo these people seeing your ads are going to be<strong>very likely to purchase or sign up</strong>because theyve already been to your website and are most likely interested in what you have to offer.\r\n<h4 id=\"GetStarted\">How to Get Started</h4>\r\nIn order to build a custom audience from people who have purchased from you or<strong>visited your website</strong>(which are some of the best kind of people by the way  it makes sense, theyve raised their hand and shown an interest in what you have to offer as a business), you need install a<strong>Facebook Pixel</strong>.\r\n\r\n<i>*This part you might need to be a little technically inclined for or send this guide to someone who is.</i>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<blockquote>How to Install your Facebook Pixel (Free Guide)\r\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/business/help/952192354843755\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.facebook.com/business/help/952192354843755</a></blockquote>\r\n<i>The page will look something like this:</i>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-5042 size-full\" src=\"http://codelabstudios.com/app/uploads/2018/02/Facebook-Pixel-Guide-min.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"728\" height=\"447\" />\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h5 id=\"Audience\">How to Create the Audience</h5>\r\n<blockquote><span class=\"popout\">Visit your Facebook Ads Manager\r\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ads/manager/\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.facebook.com/business/help/952192354843755</a></span></blockquote>\r\nOnce youre in your<strong>Facebook Ads Manager</strong>, go ahead and click on the<img src=\"https://codelabstudios.dev/app/uploads/2017/08/Hamburger.jpg\" />and follow the instructions in the images below.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-5041\" src=\"http://codelabstudios.com/app/uploads/2018/02/Steps-1-and-2-min.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"734\" height=\"268\" />\r\n\r\nAnd thats basically it for the basics on setting up a custom audience for remarketing.\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h6 id=\"Conclusion\">Conclusion</h6>\r\nThis is just the beginners guide on<strong>what is Facebook Remarketing &amp; How to get Started</strong>. It gets complicated from here when it comes down to targeting the audience, creating ads, A/B testing campaigns, optimizing for conversions, getting people to actually buy from you, and scaling up. If youre not careful, you can waste money.\r\n<blockquote><span class=\"popout\">If Facebook Advertising sounds like something youd want to look into, give us a call and get some free advice.</span></blockquote>\r\n&nbsp;','What is Facebook Remarketing and is it Important?','','inherit','closed','closed','','4191-revision-v1','','','2018-02-14 05:18:47','2018-02-14 10:18:47','',4191,'http://codelabstudios.com/4191-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(5045,1,'2018-02-14 05:19:06','2018-02-14 10:19:06','<header class=\"entry-header\"></header>\r\n<div class=\"entry-content content\">\r\n<div id=\"cs-content\" class=\"cs-content\">\r\n<div id=\"x-section-1\" class=\"x-section\">\r\n<div class=\"x-container max width\">\r\n<div class=\"x-column x-sm x-1-1\">\r\n<div class=\"x-text\">\r\n\r\nSo if youre interested in advertising on Facebook in 2017, you<strong>should first know<